title: HANGAR 128! STELLAR 3RD FLR 2X1 APT READY FOR MOVE IN
posting_body: ['WELCOME TO HANGAR 128 APARTMENTS!', 'Allow our fresh and unique homes to be the runway for your life in Everett, Washington!', 'Perfectly located next to I5 and just north of Seattle, walking distance to shopping, Metro Park and Ride, and multiple other conveniences.', 'The community is also located just minutes from Boeing and Paine Field.', 'Our homes offer sophisticated schemes, wood-like flooring, rich espresso cabinetry, and designer kitchens with custom tile backsplash.', 'The heart of our community, the new community lounge, replicates a classic airplane hangar featuring a full kitchen, fireplace, and direct access to the pool.', 'We are looking forward to your arrival, and can’t wait to show you around!', 'Call the leasing office today for your personal tour!', 'Hangar 128 is the perfect takeoff and landing place for your day-to-day life.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Use this link for more info:', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 846 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Fireplace', '- High-Speed Internet Access', '- Range', '- Disposal', '- Washer/Dryer', '- Handrails', '- Designer Finishes and Details', '- Heating', '- Refrigerator', '- Dishwasher', '- Storage Units', 'Community Amenities', '- 10 Acres of Rich Landscaping', '- Several BBQ Areas', '- 4 blocks from I-5', '- Outdoor Pool', '- Resident Lounge and Internet Cafe', '- Reserved Parking', '- Unmatched Management Services', '- One Block From Metro Park & Ride', '- Airplane Hangar Inspired Clubhouse', '- Package Service', '- Tranquil Park-Like Setting', '- Covered Parking', '- BRAND NEW Fitness Center', '- One Block from Mariner Park & Ride', '- Pet-centric Community', '- Under 10 Minutes to Boeing', '- Grocery Store Walking Distance', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet friendly, contact for details.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday-Sunday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Hangar 128', '13031 8th Ave W, Everett, WA, 98204', 'QlDtJb9a']
